195
00:10:43.135 --> 00:10:45.535
Handuk dengan kepiting bulu kuda dari Danau Suwa?

196
00:10:45.535 --> 00:10:47.935
Ya, "Su wa ko" (Danau Suwa), "Ke ga ni" (kepiting bulu kuda)

197
00:10:47.935 --> 00:10:50.335
